<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200806/58d784e9faff4da2a18c807ed266483f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/4ce1e9e36c1c44b1b3bb790bff88dc34.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">魔都惊现一家「<strong>火焰生蚝火锅</strong>」，<strong>专做会“喷火”的乳山生蚝</strong>！上桌后，等待服务员倒入米酒，再用点火器一点...小伙伴们快掏出手机抖音预定一条！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200806/8d63a189504043488a1b7f58a805eefa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">居然还能“<strong>一锅3吃</strong>”，吃生蚝、涮火锅、烤肉，统统满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 锅底自带3斤生蚝 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200806/b845dd195ac74e41af6772ffead62f8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整锅生蚝一起上，出场就霸气十足！<strong>锅底自带3斤生蚝</strong>。有蒜蓉、香辣、酸菜<strong>3种底锅可以选</strong>，这次深扒妹选的香辣锅~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 每一只都饱满回甜 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/6dbef7a8cf7c475ea0c78246a24aa0d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">等生蚝微微开口，就能尝鲜儿了！<strong>每一只都肥沃饱满</strong>，每一口都是海的味道，吃完嘴里<strong>还有一丝丝回甜</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 专设10℃海鲜养殖区 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/c6621cf0fe114844b93bacac68a1ec51.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每天空运来的生蚝都还不够卖！店内的<strong>海鲜养殖水温严格控制在10℃</strong>，只为锁住最新鲜的味道！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 现洗现开！每日空运的乳山生蚝 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/53d8285c403a4502ad2ae9dfb849b5f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200806/b85e0a1b88a645a5818347ce71caba2b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内坚持<strong>每日空运活蚝</strong>，只选高品质的<strong>乳山生蚝</strong>！现洗现开，每只生蚝都是<strong>人工手刷</strong>，刚开盖都能感觉到它们在“<strong>呼吸</strong>”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200806/ff5c94158d3c410b93c119a9582c0646.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200806/3e21109c6bac45e88629ad6fe215cb7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一边吃生蚝，还能一边涮火锅。倒入<strong>熬制5小时的骨汤</strong>，高汤和生蚝的鲜味完美结合，简直是对味蕾的双重享受~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 边涮火锅边“兼职”烤肉 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/c1ff3b4fcdc94562a7f2e7d902bc9fb0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嗨吃火锅的同时，<strong>还能“兼职”吃烤肉</strong>，<strong>40+种菜品</strong>边涮边烤，这次终于一次性get美食的双重快乐了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 涮火锅必点 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/cf26bdaa8d8445758dd1c9d6ad394bab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/ba2dcd9dfa164a8fb3406fb7cd5e8916.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>火锅cp必点的毛肚</strong>，红汤里七上八下后，脆爽无比！<strong>牛部位上乘的牛上脑</strong>，不仅片得很大，肥瘦适中，给了舌尖无与伦比的满足感~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/ae4036782fe84dcf923ce82071d6c209.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200806/1f2a493fab8a43dda19ef9595e1d5b0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">澳洲进口的雪花牛肉，<strong>大理石纹路清晰可见</strong>，肥瘦搭配刚刚好~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/69fd802b689f414fb225c506fd0686a6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200806/189bc5d4d6164b08a639f3322987385f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有五花肉、牛上脑......<strong>品种丰富</strong>，<strong>肉质鲜嫩</strong>，看着烤盘上“滋滋”的肉，就开始垂涎了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 点锅底就送生滚粥 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200806/583e21b66c1342eb8026ceb57bf515d2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">敲重点啦！只要点锅底（点香锅、生蚝锅）就<strong>送地道广式生滚粥</strong>，稀稠适中、口感香滑绵润~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 还有鸳鸯火锅汤底 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/b7a44288d75249ef9eb5bd0af38fc435.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内还有别的火锅汤底的哦。红锅都是<strong>从重庆运来的手工炒制底料</strong>，刚煮开就能闻到香辣味！清锅是熬制5h的骨汤，鲜味绝了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/7c6e367b8e3c418db75e971c273d0d94.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200806/d2b1e69cb82a40158d028711757fd174.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内招牌必点当然是卤味蒸笼了！这里的卤味要用<strong>20+种卤料</strong>，<strong>慢卤12小时</strong>，卤至入味，直到软糯~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/ce0b3f1407d24adaadfe5fc31e4c85bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤牛蛙、卤牛百叶、卤花蛤、卤黄喉、卤鸭头、卤八爪鱼、卤土豆......各种卤味应有尽有！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 晚了就吃不到！卤牛蛙 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/7a7c3bef1a7446b39ad0b7882f2b5780.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤牛蛙每次超抢手，<strong>稍微晚一点就吃不到了</strong>。蛙腿肉软嫩而有嚼头，吃了一个又一个，停不下来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 超弹牙！卤八爪鱼 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200806/1b5f47c39fa74372aec86cd6afe3bebf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤香入味的八爪鱼，简直是<strong>肉香版的QQ糖</strong>，嚼起来很是弹牙~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200806/4d8f51a3906b4aa683d5b765e54a254b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">半夜才打烊的夜宵档，<strong>只做炭火现烤的地道烧烤</strong>！看着滋滋冒烟的名场面，烟火气很是浓郁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200806/084378fc14f3440981f57a7be28c471a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤羊肉串先刷酱再撒料，老板说这样才能锁住汁水又入味！每一串都肥瘦相间，外焦内嫩，<strong>咬下去的瞬间感觉汁水在舌尖爆炸</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200806/c3234fa0b55a4ce49943fc1b07b8d2fa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>\\\</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/89fd9dd34e204359958bdf9a1e221185.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被满满金银蒜蓉盖住的扇贝和生蚝，还没出炉就香气满溢了~扇贝肉混着汁水，裹着蒜蓉粉丝的全部塞进嘴里，也太满足了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 还有这些解腻神器 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/d25e0454265445388359a2702cf161b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里的糖水也超圈粉，水果布丁、水果烧仙草......各种口味选择超多，每一碗都很精致，是<strong>解腻神器</strong>没错了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看完这一波“<strong>夜宵打卡攻略</strong>”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是都迫不及待想打卡了呢？</p>
